<ul>
<li>Buy a Roma Pass for discounted entry into many museums and archaeological sites plus free public transport for 48 or 72 hours</li>
<li>Head to Aventine Hill for a unique view of St. Peter's Basilica through a keyhole</li>
<li>Remember to toss a coin into the Trevi Fountain to ensure your return to Rome - nearly €700,000 worth of coins are thrown in each year!</li>
